        "created_at": "2019-09-23T20:18:31.317Z",
        "cooked": "<p>According to the website FoundationDB requires 4GB</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://apple.github.io/foundationdb/configuration.html#system-requirements\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://apple.github.io/foundationdb/configuration.html#system-requirements</a></p>\n<p>Can someone explain why it needs so much and what would happen if I only have 1 GB with SSD mode?</p>\n<p>Also wouldn\u2019t the requirements depend if I am using SSD or Memory Mode,  why don\u2019t the requirements take this into account?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 3,
        "updated_at": "2019-09-23T20:18:31.317Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
