        "username": "ajbeamon",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.foundationdb.org/ajbeamon/{size}/13_2.png",
        "created_at": "2019-09-24T20:43:40.869Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t remember all the history here, but it\u2019s possible the 4GB requirement was meant to represent a rough idea of what you might need to install the packages on a machine and run some simple workloads against the resulting cluster. I don\u2019t think it\u2019s required to have the full 8GB for simple cases like that. For production, though, I agree that the listed requirement should probably be higher.</p>",
